Get Catch or Numbers-at-Age by Age Groups

get_atage_groups.Rd

Process MSE simulation results for -at-age by specified age groups.

Usage

get_atage_groups(
  model_runs,
  extra_columns,
  hcr_filter,
  om_filter,
  q,
  age_groups,
  group_names,
  group_abbs,
  spinup_years = 64,
  summarise = FALSE,
  make_segments = FALSE
)

Arguments

model_runs

list of completed MSE simulation objects

extra_columns

additional columns to append to output

q

either "caa" (for catch-at-age) or "naa" (for numbers-at-age)

age_groups

ages that define age groups (3 groups required)

group_names

names for each age group

group_abbs

abbreviated names for each age group

summarise

whether to summarise across simualtions or not

make_segments

whether to generate data.frame of segment for use in plotting
